# ATA IR Portal Alert Action settings

action.ataportal = [0|1]
* Enable sending Security Events to ATA Portal

action.ataportal.param.title = <string>
* Enable overriding the title of the incident created

action.ataportal.param.group_by = <string>
* Enabling different grouping than default (hostname) of the incidents

action.ataportal.param.type = <string>
* Type of Security Event

action.ataportal.param.priority = <string>
* Priority of the Security Event

action.ataportal.param.category = <string>
* Category of the Security Event

